---
title: HelloHero: Double Honey-Herb Chicken Strips & Slaw with Creamy Parsnip-Potato Salad
description: Here comes the much-loved flavour combination of sweet and sour. Take your chicken dinner to new levels by coating it in lemon and honey. A creamy potato salad on the side and everyone will be surprised by how irresistible this dish is. Who wants seconds?

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
